ally, an effect we suggest could arise\nwhen individual dust clumps become optically-thick at the highest mass-loss\nrates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Aug 2012 21:34:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
