al\nsignal-to-noise ratio of the subsequent EPI time series at the expense of a\nsmall increase in overall acquisition time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 Aug 2012 01:24:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-07"}
